		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Go to 18 416&#xD;&#xA;- Get through the goblins by playing as a drow and forcing them to leave&#xD;&#xA;- Go to the back of the windmill (-11 428) and flick the release brake lever&#xD;&#xA;- Talk to the gnome" />
